{"id":876096,"date":[{"year":1992,"month":7,"day":20}],"page":"5","source":"旖旎、悠远的情思(二首)","region":"","masthead":"笔会","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"316","ytitle":"","mtitle":"笔会","ftitle":"","authors":["谢聪"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢聪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄鹤楼之谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏日，我坐在那由诗谣组合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而成的小船，漂行。沿途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听见许多陶瓷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迸裂发出的和鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细声细气的风，使远处的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄鹤楼朦胧起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江在云霓转身时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不停地向我堆撒浪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花里，我骑着遥远的古梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨柳和仿宋街坊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我装饰文化，为我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抖擞精神，引导传说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空于是半开，太阳在广袤的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树丛蜷伏。我向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这巍峨的建筑，取一叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扁舟的意境，并乞求"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"允许让那天涯落泊者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驻足"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄鹤依然无声无息。焦急的塔身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似乎越抬越高，那檐角也"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急切地越伸越弯长。呵，那只黄鹤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会悠然归来么?此刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它又穿翔在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一片云彩之中呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸳鸯瀑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云深处，轰鸣的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流泻声，无始无终"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳珠溅玉的水光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光怪陆离。一切似乎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都不必矫饰。在谁也"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感到透骨凉的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤裸裸的你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂吻着大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以震撼山峦的热情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和献身的气魄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诵读爱的宣言"}]}